電影評價褒貶不一。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度50%，平均得分5.4／10<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/maze_runner_the_scorch_trials/|title=Maze Runner: The Scorch Trials (2015)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2015-09-18|archive-date=2016-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531195245/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/maze_runner_the_scorch_trials/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分43，代表「褒貶不一及一般」的評價<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/maze-runner-the-scorch-trials|title=Maze Runner: The Scorch Trials reviews|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2015-09-17|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923154140/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/maze-runner-the-scorch-trials|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「B+」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/09/maze-runner-the-scorch-trials-black-mass-everest-captive-box-office-1201533896/|title=‘Scorch Trials’ Slows & ‘Black Mass’ Overperforms In The Face Of Fatigued Audiences – Saturday AM Box Office|work=deadline.com|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2017-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716235047/http://deadline.com/2015/09/maze-runner-the-scorch-trials-black-mass-everest-captive-box-office-1201533896/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

